headline: BMO Capital Maintains Market Perform rating on Autodesk (ADSK), Lifts PT
summary: On May 23, BMO Capital Markets adjusted its stance on Autodesk, Inc. (NASDAQ:ADSK)’s stock, raising its price objective to $333 from the prior target of $324, while maintaining a “Market Perform” rating. The decision was backed by the company’s healthy start to FY 2026, exceeding expectations with its billings and offering favourable commentary related to […]
